    <item>
      <title>香港对市场操纵者判处创纪录监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hk-court-hands-out-longest-jail-time-for-market-manipulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据主审法官称，香港法院以市场操纵罪判处两名被告六年零八个月监禁，这是香港迄今为止对此类罪行判处的最长刑期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hk-court-hands-out-longest-jail-time-for-market-manipulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:32:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾总统呼吁“国家认同”可能激怒中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/taiwan-s-lai-risks-angering-china-with-national-identity-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾总统赖清德呼吁执政党更好地培养民众对这个民主治理岛屿的归属感，他的言论有可能恶化他与中国大陆的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/taiwan-s-lai-risks-angering-china-with-national-identity-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受政治担忧影响，LG 推迟与通用汽车在美国建设电动汽车电池工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lg-slows-ev-cell-plant-with-gm-in-us-as-political-worries-swirl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电动汽车需求低迷，且外国公司担心美国政治变化，韩国电池制造商 LG Energy Solution Ltd. 正在放缓与通用汽车公司在密歇根州合作建设第三家工厂的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lg-slows-ev-cell-plant-with-gm-in-us-as-political-worries-swirl</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:43:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度有望削减税收以缩小财政缺口：预算指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/india-seen-curbing-fiscal-deficit-cutting-taxes-budget-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度新联合政府的首份预算中，预计总理纳伦德拉·莫迪将坚持控制财政赤字的计划，同时仍将削减税收并增加福利支出以让盟友满意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/india-seen-curbing-fiscal-deficit-cutting-taxes-budget-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:19:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔·拜登向希望他下台的民主党人屈服，颠覆美国政坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-22/biden-drops-out-plunging-2024-us-election-into-uncharted-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将接力棒交给卡马拉·哈里斯是一笔 9600 万美元的赌注，赌她能在历史上最短的总统竞选中为竞选注入活力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-22/biden-drops-out-plunging-2024-us-election-into-uncharted-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总统退出竞选后，世界各国领导人赞扬拜登的政绩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/world-leaders-praise-biden-s-record-after-president-steps-aside</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登宣布自己 11 月不会竞选连任后，世界各国领导人纷纷向他致敬。他是自 1968 年以来第一位退出总统竞选的现任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/world-leaders-praise-biden-s-record-after-president-steps-aside</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出使特朗普贸易面临不确定性，大选重新开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/biden-exit-leaves-markets-asking-what-s-next-for-trump-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周以来，投资者一直在押注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，减持长期美国债券，购买比特币等。现在，他们正在考虑乔·拜登退出竞选是否会增加民主党获胜的几率——以及他们必须在多大程度上重新调整他们的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/biden-exit-leaves-markets-asking-what-s-next-for-trump-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 19:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾与中国就临时海域协议细节存在分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/philippines-china-reach-understanding-on-disputed-sea-missions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在宣布该协议数小时后，菲律宾和中国已就一项管理马尼拉南海军事前哨补给任务的“临时安排”的细节产生分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/philippines-china-reach-understanding-on-disputed-sea-missions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:05:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平誓言重塑中国财政，帮助负债地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/xi-vows-more-local-government-support-in-new-economic-blueprint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平公布了一系列计划，旨在为负债累累的地方政府提供财政支持。与此同时，执政党中国共产党宣布了中国作为世界第二大经济体的长期发展蓝图，其中几乎没有什么重大意外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/xi-vows-more-local-government-support-in-new-economic-blueprint</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
